cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this work, please cite it as below."
title: "Capability-Bounded Agents: Provable, Injection-Resistant Action Limits for Autonomous LLM Agents"
authors:
  - family-names: "Ale"
    given-names: "Narendar Kumar"
    email: "nale02820@ucumberlands.edu"
    affiliation: "University of the Cumberlands"
abstract: >
  A reference monitor and capability contract construction giving provable,
  injection-resistant containment (0% bypass) for bounded actions taken by
  autonomous LLM agents, regardless of model output. Includes a mechanism
  benchmark and a paper draft; the companion real-model adversarial
  evaluation is at https://github.com/NarenderKumarA/capability-bounded-agents-eval.
repository-code: "https://github.com/NarenderKumarA/capability-bounded-agents"
license: MIT
date-released: 2026-07-20
keywords:
  - prompt injection
  - AI agent safety
  - reference monitor
  - capability-based security
  - LLM security
